txt.en: 'I will need some supplies for this journey that I hope to take back to Nurn. We should see if there are any supplies and rations to gather in Orodir.'
The prison fortress of Naerband has been rounding up anyone and everyone in an effort to enforce a twisted law over the lands.

'This food and these supplies should assist us on our long journey. Even the Maegond Spur is not without treachery, and the Sea of Nurn is too vast and deadly to risk sailing across.\n\n'Do not worry. This is the path we must take, just as you have taken your own path.'
Akhrûn can be found just outside of Orodir, next to Naerband.\n\nYou should speak with Akhrûn.
Orodir is located next to Naerband.\n\nYou should collect supplies and rations for the Nurnhoth.
